6. Verify payment card step 2
This is a safety precaution to make sure there is money on the account.
The amount you've chosen will be temporarily reserved on your card but is never
transferred from your card. When the charging is finished the actual amount
that you’ve charged for will be deducted and the remaining amout that was
reserved will be released on your card. Depending on your banks terms the
remaining amount will be released with various timing, it might be immediately
or it may take a few days.
Please make sure that your card
is open for international payment. Credit cards from Visa or MasterCard will
work, at this time unfortunately American Express is not going to work.
