Together with the Chalmers University of Technology
Göteborg Energi and Chalmers deepen their cooperation with the goal of research contributing to sustainable energy systems. Initially, it is about smart electricity networks, energy efficiency in buildings, energy combining (production of electricity, heat, fuel, and others), transport and energy.
Göteborg Energi is more than your common energy company. We are Gothenburg’s own energy company and are owned by the City of Gothenburg. In addition to creating sustainable and safe solutions in energy and fiber, we also work for a bigger goal - a more sustainable Gothenburg.
+46 31-62 62 62
